title: 2- Bedroom Apartment Rental in Quiet Building
posting_body: QR Code Link to This Post   This is a 2-Bedroom, Kitchen, Dinning room, Patio with beautiful view of Woodridge Golf Course. Available July 1st, 2022. Credit Check $50.00.
